  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个连接状态机的图，描述客户端从建立连接到关闭的完整生命周期。起点是INIT，然后进入HANDSHAKING握手阶段。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "INIT",
        "HANDSHAKING",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，从初始状态到INIT，然后HANDSHAKING。请问握手成功后怎么转移到正常状态？是通过on_connected吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HANDSHAKING",
        "on_connected"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，HANDSHAKING通过on_connected()进入STREAMING状态，这是正常数据传输阶段。然后STREAMING可以通过on_first_data()或on_heartbeat()保持。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HANDSHAKING",
        "STREAMING",
        "on_first_data",
        "on_heartbeat",
        "on_connected"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把STREAMING加进去了，还有自循环的on_frame_sent()，这个表示发送数据帧后还在STREAMING状态，但可能有ACK pending。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "STREAMING",
        "on_frame_sent",
        "ACK pending"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来需要优雅关闭的流程。STREAMING收到on_eof_sent()或on_eof_received()后进入DRAINING状态，这时候要等未完成的ACK。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "STREAMING",
        "DRAINING",
        "on_eof_sent",
        "on_eof_received"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "DRAINING状态我理解了，它也有自循环表示pending ACKs remain。那什么时候能到TERMINATED？是on_ack且没有pending的时候吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DRAINING",
        "TERMINATED",
        "on_ack",
        "pending"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。另外错误处理也很重要——HANDSHAKING、STREAMING、DRAINING任何一个阶段遇到on_error()都要进入FAILED状态，STREAMING还有heartbeat timeout的情况。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HANDSHAKING",
        "STREAMING",
        "DRAINING",
        "FAILED",
        "on_error",
        "heartbeat timeout"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。TERMINATED和FAILED都指向终止节点[*]。整个状态流转已经画好了，从INIT到最终结束的所有路径都覆盖了。",
